-- (2026-04-23, agent-orchestration-monitoring_20260423) Buffered channels (capacity 10) for register/unregister/broadcast prevent deadlocks. Unbuffered channels cause blocking sends that can deadlock.
-- (2026-04-23, agent-orchestration-monitoring_20260423) Async agent execution via goroutine in triggerAgent ‚Äî don't block HTTP response.
